Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki has asked for your help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, Ryuuzaki has asked for your help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to help, we need you to come here as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was thinking of how to start discussing the subject with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that they would approach me with this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this manner, I'll be able to investigate both the Investigative Headquarters and the fake Kira as much as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it takes, I've got to find the fake Kira before they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem; {\alpha&HFF&}after all, we both want to catch Kira, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem; after all, we both want to catch Kira, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me "Ryuuzaki" while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does that make me "Asahi Light"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, That is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're here, I'll call you "Light-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for throwing you in at the deep end, {\alpha&HFF&}but I need you to look over all the current material we have on the investigation, including the videos that were sent to the Japanese TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for throwing you in at the deep end, but I need you to look over all the current material we have on the investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}including the videos that were sent to the Japanese TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for throwing you in at the deep end, but I need you to look over all the current material we have on the investigation, including the videos that were sent to the Japanese TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I can't let you take any of the material away, or make notes of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.80,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,384)}Last night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... {\alpha&HFF&}we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But won't it be hard for us to investigate with him if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But won't it be hard for us to investigate with him if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. {\alpha&HFF&}What's the point in him helping us in this investigation anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. What's the point in him helping us in this investigation anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we only need to hide this from him till we've heard his opinions on these videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun's skills of deduction are truly quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees these videos, {\alpha&HFF&}he may be able to deduce that this is the work of a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees these videos, he may be able to deduce that this is the work of a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the basis for claiming that there is a second Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}you say that the victims of the predicted murders were ones Kira wouldn't normally have killed, "since they only committed minor crimes",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the basis for claiming that there is a second Kira... you say that the victims of the predicted murders were ones Kira wouldn't normally have killed, "since they only committed minor crimes",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that theory of yours is the only basis we have, isn't it Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, we've assumed that Kira needs a face and a name in order to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, from the fact that Ukita-san was killed when he happened to rush to the TV station that time... {\alpha&HFF&}and from the fact that Kira spoke as if they could kill L merely by having him appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, from the fact that Ukita-san was killed when he happened to rush to the TV station that time... and from the fact that Kira spoke as if they could kill L merely by having him appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can come to the conclusion that the second Kira can kill people merely by seeing their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, after reviewing the case and watching these videos, Light-kun is able to deduce that there is a second Kira, the majority of my suspicions against him will be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evident that Kira wants to kill the L who has been leading the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things continue to progress as they are, I will die after appearing on TV in three days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that Kira would let an opportunity like this pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if my son doesn't manage to deduce that there is a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean that your suspicions will deepen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}If that happens, my suspicions will remain at 5% or lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If that happens, my suspicions will remain at 5% or lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reveal to him that we're investigating the possibility of a second Kira, and have him assist us with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:45.23,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you have understood from this that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:51.68,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,On the date and time specified...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... {\alpha&HFF&}the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... {\alpha&HFF&}is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far more serious than a simple drop in my image as Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:05:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why has no one offered any explanations for any of these videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something odd going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I better not say anything stupid regarding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave things as they are, L will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going, Light-kun? {\alpha&HFF&}Have you been able to deduce anything from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going, Light-kun? Have you been able to deduce anything from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that there's more than one person who has Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-{\alpha&HFF&}Kira's power? What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kira's power? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kira's power? What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a high probability that this is not the same Kira that we've been dealing with until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, there's a high probability that this is not the same Kira that we've been dealing with until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira we've been dealing with until now would not have utilized the suspects used in this broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the fact that if Kira does indeed need a name and a face to kill, {\alpha&HFF&}it's strange that they were able to kill the policemen who merely happened to go to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the fact that if Kira does indeed need a name and a face to kill, it's strange that they were able to kill the policemen who merely happened to go to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... {\alpha&HFF&}I mean, that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... I mean, {\alpha&HFF&}that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... I mean, that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Well done, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well done, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspicions against you should now be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light-kun. {\alpha&HFF&}We also believe that there's a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light-kun. We also believe that there's a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew, Ryuuga? {\alpha&HFF&}I mean.. Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew, Ryuuga? I mean.. Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were testing me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the only one to have come up with the "second Kira" theory, people may have trouble believing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've come to the same conclusion as I did, it's become a much more convincing viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, you really are extremely helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, we have to stop the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evidently, they sympathize with Kira, but they aren't very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might even obey the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a good chance that we might be able to stop them by sending them a message from the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, there's a good chance that we might be able to stop them by sending them a message from the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have expected nothing less from you, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also thinking of that as the best course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you, Light-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}to play the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you, Light-kun, to play the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}With your talent, it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. With your talent, it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, we don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you write a response from "Kira" ready to be aired on this evening's news?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you planned all along? {\alpha&HFF&}Is that why you brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you planned all along? Is that why you brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think I became Kira, just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very good... but unless you take out the bit that says, "I don't mind if you kill L"... I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. If I were in Kira's shoes, in the current situation, I'm sure I'd order L's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke. {\alpha&HFF&}You can change it to whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke. You can change it to whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aihara-san, {\alpha&HFF&}the report is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aihara-san, the report is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible thing has occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In response to the videos sent in by Kira and aired on Sakura TV, messages have been received from another person claiming that they are the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have demanded that the message from the real Kira is broadcast on all TV channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police Headquarters have agreed for the video to be broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kira? {\alpha&HFF&}Or are they both Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kira? Or are they both Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take a look at this video sent in by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.92,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I got a response from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:39.00,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the real Kira, and those videos sent to Sakura TV were not from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.29,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, I will tolerate the actions of the one that is taking my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:49.80,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,They have worked on my behalf, and have tried to aid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.93,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}taking the lives of innocent people is directly against my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:55.71,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, taking the lives of innocent people is directly against my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:07.54,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person taking my name holds the same beliefs as I, and is willing to help me, they must stop acting impulsively, and learn to understand my true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... Video, video!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}hidden lines
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:12.90,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not heed this warning, you will leave me with no choice but to pass judgement on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm gonna send a response to Kira right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I'm gonna send a response to Kira right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.95,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,393)}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}We've received a response from the second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! We've received a response from the second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the envelope and everything else over as soon as I can; {\alpha&HFF&}for the moment, I'm sending a copy to your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the envelope and everything else over as soon as I can; for the moment, I'm sending a copy to your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.07,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira-san, {\alpha&HFF&}thank you for your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.33,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira-san, thank you for your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.00,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do as you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will do as you ask", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether I can use them or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they truly understood Kira's feelings, {\alpha&HFF&}they should have enforced L's appearance on TV, and killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they truly understood Kira's feelings, they should have enforced L's appearance on TV, and killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess things up... {\alpha&HFF&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess things up... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.95,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet you, Kira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:05.75,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that you have the eyes, but don't worry, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this idiot thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about the Shinigami's eyes on a video that's being broadcast to the entire nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they just say, "I don't believe that you have the eyes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:22.22,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think of a way that we can meet without the police finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.13,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we meet, {\alpha&HFF&}we can confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.42,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we meet, we can confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is hopeless... {\alpha&HFF&}If I don't do something fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is hopeless... If I don't do something fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me... {\alpha&HFF&}that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me... that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me.. {\alpha&HFF&}that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me.. that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that they exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that Shinigami actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Ryuuzaki. There's no way that Shinigami actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira used prisoners to write sentences about Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, {\alpha&HFF&}shouldn't we consider this to be the work of the original Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, shouldn't we consider this to be the work of the original Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same words from the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira we have dealt with until now wouldn't have replied to our video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira wouldn't have bought this story. And they wouldn't have prevented L from going on TV to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, {\alpha&HFF&}and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's any chance of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is correct. {\alpha&HFF&}If Kira is involved, I doubt that they'd stop trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is correct. If Kira is involved, I doubt that they'd stop trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This second Kira appears to be acting on their own interests, rather than Kira's beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, {\alpha&HFF&}their desire to meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, their desire to meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are acting on their own curiosity about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps "Shinigami" is referring to their ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami", could mean that they'll confirm each other's identity by demonstrating their ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we can consider "Shinigami" as a common term of some significance between Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to try to clarify that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will we reply again to guide them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we probe too deeply, {\alpha&HFF&}they may realize that we know nothing, and that we aren't really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we probe too deeply, they may realize that we know nothing, and that we aren't really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}From now on, we'll leave it to Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. From now on, we'll leave it to Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that having received a reply from Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}the second Kira is now content about the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that having received a reply from Kira, the second Kira is now content about the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They believe that they've successfully appealed to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they are using words that only they would know the significance of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll repeat this reply on the 6:00pm news on Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira will be watching to view the interaction between the second Kira and the fake Kira that we've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira would want to avoid any contact between the second Kira and the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll get a response from the real Kira this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, we'll get a response from the real Kira this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if we don't receive a response from Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}I've tried to think of what the second Kira would do in this situation, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've tried to think of what the second Kira would do in this situation, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would probably tell the police and the public further information that Kira would not want them to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to force Kira to seek an audience with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even more interesting if Kira does fear such a response, and sends their own message by video.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that does happen, we'll have more physical evidence against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the time being, {\alpha&HFF&}let us pursue the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the time being, let us pursue the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. That's so hot, Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired... {\alpha&HFF&}Being a model is all about having stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired... Being a model is all about having stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami need to have a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Shinigami to play with humans, they need to have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami, Ryuk, who gave a notebook to Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}tricked the Shinigami Overlord and got a second notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami, Ryuk, who gave a notebook to Kira, tricked the Shinigami Overlord and got a second notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}The Shinigami Overlord isn't that easy to trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The Shinigami Overlord isn't that easy to trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you manage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rare in the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the few who actually knows how to kill a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you killed a Shinigami, and gave Misa their notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be there when a Shinigami died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}tell me how to kill a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me how to kill a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to kill a Shinigami is... {\alpha&HFF&}to make them fall in love with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to kill a Shinigami is... to make them fall in love with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful way to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a Shinigami named Jealous, who used to constantly gaze at one particular girl from his place in the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Shinigami world, Jealous was always, always, watching that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's today, isn't it? {\alpha&HFF&}That girl's life runs out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's today, isn't it? That girl's life runs out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems so full of life... {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder why it's today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems so full of life... I wonder why it's today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... {\alpha&HFF&}why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also became curious as to how she would die, {\alpha&HFF&}so I chose to watch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also became curious as to how she would die, so I chose to watch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking alone late at night... {\alpha&HFF&}and then.. suddenly a man appeared from an alley, and confessed his love for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking alone late at night... and then.. {\alpha&HFF&}suddenly a man appeared from an alley, and confessed his love for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking alone late at night... and then.. suddenly a man appeared from an alley, and confessed his love for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more than anyone in this world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch over, and protect you forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl, having never seen the man before, {\alpha&HFF&}naturally refused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl, having never seen the man before, naturally refused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll kill you... before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll kill you... {\alpha&HFF&}before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll kill you... before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}Stop that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous did something that no Shinigami should ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous used his Death Note to save that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami exist solely to take human lives in order to increase their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, {\alpha&HFF&}Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... {\alpha&HFF&}and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous's life was added to the lifespan of the girl he had been watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't in love with that girl, {\alpha&HFF&}he wouldn't have died?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't in love with that girl, he wouldn't have died?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... {\alpha&HFF&}who helped me back then... was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... who helped me back then... {\alpha&HFF&}was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... who helped me back then... was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous was in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that notebook is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}You've got to make a Shinigami fall in love and help someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You've got to make a Shinigami fall in love and help someone.
