Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Rem? You aren't falling for me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. {\alpha&HFF&}You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. You can't kill me.
